Google Photos Sony A7III RAW Backup /!/ I'm backing up my photos to google photos to have a quick lookup and browse of past pictures. I see that the google backup and sync app alerts me that it "Can't convert photos to high quality", "They will continue to be stored as original quality in Google Drive using X GB of storage". I also look on the [Google Photos website](https://support.google.com/photos/answer/6193313?co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop&hl=en) and they say that the A7 is supported. 

Does anyone know if this support is coming in the future?
